  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Assist with restaurant's day-to-day operations.</li><li>Greet and usher guests to table, present menu and share promotional items</li><li>Take orders and serve food and beverages to guests.</li><li>Respond promptly and professionally to guests' needs, questions, concerns.</li><li>Housekeeping duties to maintain a neat and clean working environment.</li><li>Perform any other operational duties and responsibilities as and when assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Loves the sun and outdoor activities.</li><li>Friendly and customer oriented.</li><li>Able to work independently and take initiatives.</li><li>Able to remain calm and composed in a hectic and fast-paced environment.</li><li>Must be able to work on weekends and public holidays.</li></ul>",
